snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get Together: Explore A New World Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Get together with Clubs and explore the beautiful new World of Windenburg in The Sims 4 Get Together Expansion Pack!
 
Learn More: http://o.ea.com/47231
 
Create and join clubs, get together with other Sims for exciting group activities, and live it up in The Sims 4 Get Together Expansion Pack, available this December!
